  </a>
  <a href="#4" id="4">
   The miners are demanding more local control over their industry.
  </a>
  <a href="#5" id="5">
   Miners are demanding a 40 percent wage increase for night work, improved living conditions, a fixed day off and retirement after 20 years of underground work.
  </a>
